  </context>

  <constraints>
    <constraint source="ADR-013">AI placement: Template lives in Dataverse + `infra/insights/schemas/`. No CRUD-side caller injects orchestration internals.</constraint>
    <constraint source="ADR-015">Audit on every Tool dispatch this Template makes. Search query strings hashed in Tier 2 (not plaintext); hydrated matter ids stored as work-history record references in Tier 3.</constraint>
    <constraint source="ADR-018">Feature flag `feature.actionEngine.template.findSimilarMatters` referenced in governance block.</constraint>
    <constraint source="ADR-029">Publish size impact: zero — JSON + Dataverse seed only.</constraint>
    <constraint source="project">Validate via `jps-validate` before deployment.</constraint>
    <constraint source="project">Verify the matter-summary semantic index name + Tool id BEFORE authoring. Read `docs/architecture/AI-ARCHITECTURE.md` and task 016's deploy notes. If the index does not exist in dev, escalate as a dependency (do NOT author against a non-existent index).</constraint>
    <constraint source="project">`EvidenceRequired: true` on the optional `ExplainSimilarity` AI step. Tool dispatch layer enforces.</constraint>
    <constraint source="project">Output's `sourceCitations` includes a citation per candidate (matter id + deep-link URL). Citation discipline per design.md §7.4.5 guardrail #7.</constraint>
    <constraint source="project">Default `humanGate.required = false` — this Template only reads data, no side effects. No gate needed.</constraint>
  </constraints>

