    <patterns>
      <pattern name="JPS Action authoring with Hybrid classification" location=".claude/skills/jps-action-create/SKILL.md">Same format as task 053/054; the Template's overall classification is `Hybrid` (one AI step + one Deterministic step + one optional AI step).</pattern>
      <pattern name="Semantic search Tool invocation" location="docs/architecture/AI-ARCHITECTURE.md">Use the `SearchSemantic` Tool (or equivalent) with a `topK` + `minConfidence` parameter set. Returns ranked candidates with confidence scores.</pattern>
      <pattern name="Citation discipline" location="projects/ai-spaarke-action-engine-r1/design.md §7.4.5">Output schema's `sourceCitations` is non-optional for any Tool that returns evidence-backed results. UI renders citations as hyperlinks.</pattern>
    </patterns>
